public interface ToolkitConstants

static final short EVENT_MO_SHORT_MESSAGE_CONTROL_BY_NAA
Event : MO Short Message Control by NAA = 10. Note: The constant EVENT_MO_SHORT_MESSAGE_CONTROL_BY_SIM was erroneously used instead of the constant Event EVENT_MO_SHORT_MESSAGE_CONTROL_BY_NAA in earlier releases of this specification.
